\hypertarget{surface-mass-density}{%
\section{Surface Mass Density}\label{surface-mass-density}}

The surface mass density (SMD) is used to estimate the vertical velocity
dispersion \texttt{vertical\_velocity\_dispersion} and is defined by

\[\Sigma \left ( R \right )=2\int_{0}^{\infty}\rho \left ( R,z \right )\mathrm{d}z\]\[The surface mass density of the disc and bulge\]

